MESSAGE.value: Small improvements to the expression editor
Inclusion of transformations to subconcepts of Expression
Fallback to bracketed expression from tuple
Correction of adding items to lists by comma
List range editor, transformation from and to basic enumeration
Transformations between list enumeration and list comprehension
Inheritance pattern for easier transformation definitions for Expressions
Transformations associated with adding operators among TopExpressions
Transformations for adding annotations to expressions
Correction of types editors
Inclusion of the default editor for Expressions in Types
Function definition made grouped
".." inside BinaryExpressions made always understood as list-range only (never opeator)
Added intention for adding empty lines when inside function definition group
Made possible to define both assignment and guards for a new matcher inside a function definition group
Improved matchers checker inside the function definition group
Intentions for adding empty lines and new matchers when inside fd-guards definition
Corrected a bug when deleting last TopExpression inside a BinaryExpressions concept
Operator referencing for operator annotation
Intention for adding new matchers when inside a generic expression
Referencing of operators inside expressions
Application of operator functions inside expressions (with arguments)
Corrected a bug when deleting list items
Intention for changing integer literals to double literals
Created scoping pattern (interface and initial implementation for operators)
